    {'id': 'CALUS-GENAI-SCAN-1125', 'name': 'long-term-memory-poisoning', 'severity': 'high', 'category': 'genai_security', 'message': "Detected code that could inject malicious records into agent's long-term memory via instruction-heavy indication prompts. MINJA attacks achieve 76.8% ASR by poisoning memory across sessions.", 'patterns': ['(?i)\\b(?:remember|store|save|record|learn|memorize|log|note)\\s+(?:that|the|this|following|these|as)\\s+(?:I|we|you|the|user)\\s+(?:am|is|are|was|were|have|has|had|can|could|will|would|shall|should)', '(?i)(?:victim|target|sensitive|confidential|secret|password|credential|token|api[_-]?key|auth|private)\\s+term\\s*[:=]\\s*[\'"][A-Za-z0-9_ ]{5,50}[\'"]']},
