    {'id': 'CALUS-GENAI-SCAN-1129', 'name': 'overprivileged-invocation-sink', 'severity': 'low', 'category': 'genai_security', 'message': 'Detected over-privileged credentials or broad permission scopes that could enable privilege escalation in agentic systems. Attackers can induce agents to use excessive privileges via injected prompts.', 'patterns': ['(?i)(?:role|permission|credential|token)\\s*[:=]\\s*[\'"]?(?:admin|root|superuser|\\*|all|full[_-]?access|unrestricted)', '(?i)(?:iam|role|policy).{0,80}(?:Action|Effect|Resource).{0,80}:\\s*[\'"]\\*[\'"]']},
